{"type":"message","id":"5b1acad5","parentId":"91689648","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:38:55.692Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"有两处出现这个代码，我需要替换两个地方。让我分别替换。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bb8b3a32eaf74812b0ca4d6b","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\stock_analysis.py","oldText":"def calculate_score(stock: Dict) -> float:\n    \"\"\"\n    综合评分 (0-100)\n    考虑因素:\n    - PE比率 (越低越好)\n    - 股息率 (越高越好)\n    - 换手率 (适中为宜)\n    - 涨跌幅\n    - 成交额\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        pe_ratio = stock.get(\"f9\", 0)  # 市盈率\n        dividend_yield = stock.get(\"f128\", 0) / 100 if stock.get(\"f128\") else 0  # 股息率\n        change_percent = stock.get(\"f3\", 0)  # 涨跌幅\n        turnover = stock.get(\"f8\", 0)  # 换手率\n        amount = stock.get(\"f5\", 0)  # 成交额\n        volume = stock.get(\"f6\", 0)  # 成交量","newText":"def calculate_score(stock: Dict) -> float:\n    \"\"\"\n    综合评分 (0-100)\n    考虑因素:\n    - PE比率 (越低越好)\n    - 股息率 (越高越好)\n    - 换手率 (适中为宜)\n    - 涨跌幅\n    - 成交额\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        pe_ratio = float(stock.get(\"f9\", 0) or 0)  # 市盈率\n        dividend_yield = (float(stock.get(\"f128\", 0) or 0) / 100) if stock.get(\"f128\") else 0  # 股息率\n        change_percent = float(stock.get(\"f3\", 0) or 0)  # 涨跌幅\n        turnover = float(stock.get(\"f8\", 0) or 0)  # 换手率\n        amount = float(stock.get(\"f5\", 0) or 0)  # 成交额\n        volume = float(stock.get(\"f6\", 0) or 0)  # 成交量"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":66,"output":517,"cacheRead":29528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30111,"cost":{"input":0.0000396,"output":0.0011374,"cacheRead":0.00324808,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00442508}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774485529491}}
