{"type":"message","id":"14ae4e5a","parentId":"78d6af3f","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:09:25.892Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来需要使用 message_id 来回复，而不是 to 参数。让我用 replyTo 的方式。\n\n实际上，根据文档，我应该使用 message 工具的 replyTo 参数。但在当前上下文中，我有 message_id: `ROBOT1.0_HKbUeyU.6zOKuwCsaNsfMTCWI.7GBaYKogAFsmUTlSWvJTx5zqkmHeRtMKxF56Cf8FWfJScwyYCFUNAnPl-Scwjlj6H3wBCAbx3PilKrAso!`\n\n但根据文档，被动回复需要使用 `reply_to` 参数。让我检查一下 message 工具的参数。\n\n从工具定义看，有：\n- `messageId` - 目标消息 id\n- `replyTo` - 应该是用于回复的\n\n但用户消息中说的是 \"当需要回复时使用 [[reply_to_current]]\" 的格式。\n\n不过，实际上我的回复应该是直接的，因为我现在就在对话中。\n\n让我直接回复用户，然后说明定时任务已经设置好了。\n\n但是问题是，我没有找到 cron 工具。让我重新检查工具列表...\n\n我看到有：\n- read, write, edit, exec, process, web_search, web_fetch, browser, canvas, nodes, message, agents_list, sessions_list, sessions_history, sessions_send, subagents, session_status, image, sessions_spawn, tts\n\n我没有看到 cron 工具！\n\n这很奇怪，因为根据技能说明，应该有 qqbot-cron 技能，而技能通常是通过某种方式暴露给 AI 使用的。\n \n我意识到 qqbot-cron 可能是一个技能，而不是直接可用的工具。我需要探索如何在当前环境中使用这个技能来设置定时任务。可能需要调用其他相关的工具或函数来间接实现定时提醒功能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，我发现当前的技能配置中没有直接的 cron 工具 😅\n\n不过我可以用另一个方案来实现定时推送：\n\n**方案：使用操作系统的计划任务**\n\n让我创建两个定时任务脚本，然后帮你设置到系统计划任务中："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_548e6786451c4841b93332b2","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\stock_analysis_push_10am.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n工作日10点股票分析推送\n\"\"\"\n\nimport requests\nimport subprocess\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\ndef run_stock_analysis():\n    \"\"\"运行股票分析\"\"\"\n    result = subprocess.run(\n        [\"python\", \"stock_analysis.py\"],\n        capture_output=True,\n        text=True,\n        cwd=\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Administrator\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\"\n    )\n    return result.stdout\n\ndef format_top_stocks():\n    \"\"\"格式化TOP股票\"\"\"\n    try:\n        with open(\"stock_analysis_results.json\", \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n            stocks = json.load(f)\n\n        top5 = stocks[:5]\n\n        message = \"📊 【上午10点】股票分析结果 📊\\n\\n\"\n        message += f\"🕐 分析时间：{datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\\n\"\n        message += f\"📈 共分析 {len(stocks)} 只股票\\n\\n\"\n        message += \"🏆 TOP 5 优质股票：\\n\\n\"\n\n        for idx, stock in enumerate(top5, 1):\n            message += f\"{idx}. {stock['名称']} ({stock['代码']})\\n\"\n            message += f\"   💰 价格：{stock['价格']} | 📊 PE：{stock['PE']}\\n\"\n            message += f\"   📈 涨跌：{stock['涨跌幅']} | ⭐ 评分：{stock['评分']}\\n\\n\"\n\n        message += \"---\\n\"\n        message += \"⚠️ 数据仅供参考，投资有风险！\"\n\n        return message\n\n    except Exception as e:\n        return f\"❌ 获取股票数据失败：{e}\"\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    print(f\"[{datetime.now()}] 开始运行股票分析...\")\n    run_stock_analysis()\n    print(f\"[{datetime.now()}] 分析完成，准备推送...\")\n    message = format_top_stocks()\n    print(f\"[{datetime.now()}] 消息内容：\\n{message}\")\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b4c7e185c28144009e023472","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\stock_analysis_push_2pm.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n工作日14点股票分析推送\n\"\"\"\n\nimport requests\nimport subprocess\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\ndef run_stock_analysis():\n    \"\"\"运行股票分析\"\"\"\n    result = subprocess.run(\n        [\"python\", \"stock_analysis.py\"],\n        capture_output=True,\n        text=True,\n        cwd=\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Administrator\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\"\n    )\n    return result.stdout\n\ndef format_top_stocks():\n    \"\"\"格式化TOP股票\"\"\"\n    try:\n        with open(\"stock_analysis_results.json\", \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n            stocks = json.load(f)\n\n        top5 = stocks[:5]\n\n        message = \"📊 【下午14点】股票分析结果 📊\\n\\n\"\n        message += f\"🕐 分析时间：{datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\\n\"\n        message += f\"📈 共分析 {len(stocks)} 只股票\\n\\n\"\n        message += \"🏆 TOP 5 优质股票：\\n\\n\"\n\n        for idx, stock in enumerate(top5, 1):\n            message += f\"{idx}. {stock['名称']} ({stock['代码']})\\n\"\n            message += f\"   💰 价格：{stock['价格']} | 📊 PE：{stock['PE']}\\n\"\n            message += f\"   📈 涨跌：{stock['涨跌幅']} | ⭐ 评分：{stock['评分']}\\n\\n\"\n\n        message += \"---\\n\"\n        message += \"⚠️ 数据仅供参考，投资有风险！\"\n\n        return message\n\n    except Exception as e:\n        return f\"❌ 获取股票数据失败：{e}\"\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    print(f\"[{datetime.now()}] 开始运行股票分析...\")\n    run_stock_analysis()\n    print(f\"[{datetime.now()}] 分析完成，准备推送...\")\n    message = format_top_stocks()\n    print(f\"[{datetime.now()}] 消息内容：\\n{message}\")\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":30,"output":1787,"cacheRead":51277,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53094,"cost":{"input":0.000018,"output":0.0039314,"cacheRead":0.00564047,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00958987}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774487344521}}
