{"type":"message","id":"054cbc63","parentId":"39763f9c","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:11:54.885Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求配置 cron 工具。让我查看一下可用的工具列表，看看是否有 cron 相关的工具。\n\n从工具列表中，我看到有以下工具：\n- read, write, edit - 文件操作\n- exec, process - 命令执行\n- web_search, web_fetch - 网络相关\n- browser - 浏览器控制\n- canvas, nodes - 其他\n- message - 消息发送\n- agents_list, sessions_list, sessions_history, sessions_send, subagents, session_status - 会话管理\n- tts - 语音\n- sessions_spawn - 生成子会话\n- image - 图像分析\n\n我没有看到 cron 相关的工具。但是，用户提供的系统消息中提到\"工作日10点和14点，推送分析结果\"，并且系统消息中提到了\"定时提醒投递地址: channel=qqbot, to=qqbot:c2c:DB0D276754D361B0256C70255C178BD8\"。\n\n让我再看看 skill 文档中的 qqbot-cron 技能。根据 SKILL.md 的内容，它提到调用 cron 工具，但我在工具列表中没有看到 cron 工具。\n\n让我检查一下是否有其他方式。也许 cron 工具是通过其他方式访问的？\n\n或者，我应该使用 exec 命令来设置系统的 cron 任务（在 Linux 上）或者任务计划程序（在 Windows 上）。\n\n\n当前系统是 Windows，需要使用任务计划程序来替代 cron。我将探索如何在 Windows 上创建定时任务，实现每日特定时间的分析推送。主要步骤包括创建任务触发器和动作，确保在指定时间自动执行股票分析脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好！我来配置定时任务 🕙\n\n当前系统是 Windows，我会使用 Windows 任务计划程序来实现定时推送。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8388898c8c334ba6b05f1c9a","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\setup_stock_cron.ps1","content":"# Windows 任务计划设置脚本\n# 设置工作日10点和14点的股票分析推送\n\n# 检查是否以管理员权限运行\n$isAdmin = ([Security.Principal.WindowsPrincipal] [Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity]::GetCurrent()).IsInRole([Security.Principal.WindowsBuiltInRole]::Administrator)\n\nif (-not $isAdmin) {\n    Write-Host \"请以管理员权限运行此脚本\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    exit 1\n}\n\n$workspace = \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\"\n$python = \"python\"\n\nWrite-Host \"=====================================\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"设置股票分析定时任务\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"=====================================\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# 删除旧任务（如果存在）\nWrite-Host \"清理旧任务...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nschtasks /Delete /TN \"StockAnalysis_10AM\" /F 2>$null\nschtasks /Delete /TN \"StockAnalysis_2PM\" /F 2>$null\n\n# 创建10:00任务（工作日）\nWrite-Host \"创建工作日10:00定时任务...\" -ForegroundColor Green\nschtasks /Create `\n    /TN \"StockAnalysis_10AM\" `\n    /TR \"$python $workspace\\stock_analysis_push_10am.py\" `\n    /SC WEEKLY `\n    /D MON,TUE,WED,THU,FRI `\n    /ST 10:00 `\n    /F `\n    /RL HIGHEST\n\nif ($LASTEXITCODE -eq 0) {\n    Write-Host \"[OK] 10:00任务创建成功\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"[ERROR] 10:00任务创建失败\" -ForegroundColor Red\n}\n\n# 创建14:00任务（工作日）\nWrite-Host \"创建工作日14:00定时任务...\" -ForegroundColor Green\nschtasks /Create `\n    /TN \"StockAnalysis_2PM\" `\n    /TR \"$python $workspace\\stock_analysis_push_2pm.py\" `\n    /SC WEEKLY `\n    /D MON,TUE,WED,THU,FRI `\n    /ST 14:00 `\n    /F `\n    /RL HIGHEST\n\nif ($LASTEXITCODE -eq 0) {\n    Write-Host \"[OK] 14:00任务创建成功\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"[ERROR] 14:00任务创建失败\" -ForegroundColor Red\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"=====================================\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"配置完成！\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"=====================================\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"查看任务命令：\"\nWrite-Host \"schtasks /Query /TN StockAnalysis_10AM\"\nWrite-Host \"schtasks /Query /TN StockAnalysis_2PM\"\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"手动运行测试：\"\nWrite-Host \"schtasks /Run /TN StockAnalysis_10AM\"\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"删除任务：\"\nWrite-Host \"schtasks /Delete /TN StockAnalysis_10AM /F\"\nWrite-Host \"schtasks /Delete /TN StockAnalysis_2PM /F\"\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":9152,"output":1432,"cacheRead":45771,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56355,"cost":{"input":0.0054912,"output":0.0031504000000000002,"cacheRead":0.005034810000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01367641}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774487493682}}
