{"type":"message","id":"ac1aff5f","parentId":"2ff4be68","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:17:41.526Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要修改股票筛选条件，指定特定的股票代码前缀：\n- 600/601/603/605: 沪市主板\n- 000/001/002/003: 深市主板/中小板\n\n我需要修改 stock_analysis.py 脚本，在筛选股票时添加这些条件。\n\n让我先读取当前的脚本，然后修改筛选逻辑。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好！我来修改筛选条件，只分析沪市主板和深市主板的股票 🔧"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f6cf7048be3241ba9710f3bd","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\stock_analysis.py","limit":100}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":7289,"output":214,"cacheRead":54921,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62424,"cost":{"input":0.0043733999999999995,"output":0.0004708,"cacheRead":0.00604131,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010885510000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774487857178}}
{"type":"message","id":"578d40ae","parentId":"ac1aff5f","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:17:41.555Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f6cf7048be3241ba9710f3bd","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\nA股主板股票基本面+技术面综合分析\n筛选低PE、高股息、技术面良好的股票\n\"\"\"\n\nimport requests\nimport json\nimport time\nimport math\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom typing import List, Dict, Any\nimport statistics\n\n# 配置\nOUTPUT_FILE = \"stock_analysis_results.json\"\nLOG_FILE = \"stock_analysis.log\"\n\ndef log(message: str):\n    \"\"\"记录日志\"\"\"\n    timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n    line = f\"[{timestamp}] {message}\"\n    print(line)\n    with open(LOG_FILE, \"a\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n        f.write(line + \"\\n\")\n\ndef safe_float(value, default=0):\n    \"\"\"安全转换浮点数，处理None、\"-\"等无效值\"\"\"\n    if value is None or value == \"\" or value == \"-\":\n        return default\n    try:\n        return float(value)\n    except (ValueError, TypeError):\n        return default\n\ndef get_stock_list() -> List[Dict]:\n    \"\"\"获取A股主板股票列表\"\"\"\n    log(\"正在获取A股主板股票列表...\")\n    try:\n        # 使用东方财富网的股票列表API\n        url = \"https://80.push2.eastmoney.com/api/qt/clist/get\"\n        params = {\n            \"pn\": 1,\n            \"pz\": 5000,\n            \"po\": 1,\n            \"np\": 1,\n            \"ut\": \"bd1d9ddb04089700cf9c27f6f7426281\",\n            \"fltt\": 2,\n            \"invt\": 2,\n            \"fid\": \"f3\",\n            \"fs\": \"m:0+t:6,m:0+t:80,m:1+t:2,m:1+t:23\",  # 主板\n            \"fields\": \"f12,f14,f2,f3,f4,f5,f6,f7,f8,f9,f10,f11,f13,f15,f16,f17,f18,f20,f21,f23,f24,f25,f22,f33,f11,f62,f128,f136,f115,f152\"\n        }\n        headers = {\n            \"User-Agent\": \"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36\"\n        }\n\n        response = requests.get(url, params=params, headers=headers, timeout=30)\n        response.raise_for_status()\n        data = response.json()\n\n        if data.get(\"rc\") == 0 and data.get(\"data\"):\n            stocks = data[\"data\"][\"diff\"]\n            log(f\"成功获取 {len(stocks)} 只股票\")\n            return stocks\n        else:\n            log(f\"API返回异常: {data}\")\n            return []\n    except Exception as e:\n        log(f\"获取股票列表失败: {e}\")\n        return []\n\ndef calculate_score(stock: Dict) -> float:\n    \"\"\"\n    综合评分 (0-100)\n    考虑因素:\n    - PE比率 (越低越好)\n    - 股息率 (越高越好)\n    - 换手率 (适中为宜)\n    - 涨跌幅\n    - 成交额\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        pe_ratio = safe_float(stock.get(\"f9\"))  # 市盈率\n        dividend_yield = (safe_float(stock.get(\"f128\")) / 100) if stock.get(\"f128\") else 0  # 股息率\n        change_percent = safe_float(stock.get(\"f3\"))  # 涨跌幅\n        turnover = safe_float(stock.get(\"f8\"))  # 换手率\n        amount = safe_float(stock.get(\"f5\"))  # 成交额\n        volume = safe_float(stock.get(\"f6\"))  # 成交量\n\n        score = 50  # 基准分\n\n        # PE评分 (0-30分)\n        if pe_ratio > 0 and pe_ratio < 100:\n            if pe_ratio < 10:\n                score += 30\n            elif pe_ratio < 20:\n                score += 25\n            elif pe_ratio < 30:\n\n[200 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774487861552}}
{"type":"message","id":"6db87133","parentId":"578d40ae","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:17:47.865Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要修改股票筛选条件。当前脚本获取所有主板股票，但我需要添加代码前缀的筛选：\n- 600/601/603/605: 沪市主板\n- 000/001/002/003: 深市主板/中小板\n\n我需要在 get_stock_list() 或 filter_and_sort() 函数中添加筛选逻辑。最好在 filter_and_sort() 函数中添加，这样更灵活。\n\n让我先看看完整的脚本结构。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a0852a1f3ec043a39ea25822","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\stock_analysis.py","oldText":"# 配置\nOUTPUT_FILE = \"stock_analysis_results.json\"\nLOG_FILE = \"stock_analysis.log\"","newText":"# 配置\nOUTPUT_FILE = \"stock_analysis_results.json\"\nLOG_FILE = \"stock_analysis.log\"\n\n# 股票代码前缀筛选\nSTOCK_CODE_PREFIXES = [\n    \"600\", \"601\", \"603\", \"605\",  # 沪市主板\n    \"000\", \"001\", \"002\", \"003\"   # 深市主板/中小板\n]"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":919,"output":348,"cacheRead":62342,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63609,"cost":{"input":0.0005514,"output":0.0007656000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00685762,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00817462}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774487861555}}
