{"type":"message","id":"839d165b","parentId":"ce9d30d0","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:18:02.946Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要添加一个筛选函数，在 filter_and_sort() 之前调用，根据股票代码前缀进行筛选。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a6edbb9d423043469e46d8df","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\stock_analysis.py","oldText":"def filter_and_sort(stocks: List[Dict], top_n: int = 50) -> List[Dict]:\n    \"\"\"筛选并排序\"\"\"\n    log(\"正在筛选和排序...\")\n\n    # 筛选条件\n    filtered = [s for s in stocks if s[\"PE\"] > 0 and s[\"PE\"] < 100]\n\n    # 按评分排序\n    sorted_stocks = sorted(filtered, key=lambda x: x[\"评分\"], reverse=True)\n\n    # 返回前N只\n    return sorted_stocks[:top_n]","newText":"def filter_by_market(stocks: List[Dict]) -> List[Dict]:\n    \"\"\"根据市场筛选股票\"\"\"\n    log(f\"正在筛选沪市主板和深市主板股票...\")\n    filtered = []\n    for stock in stocks:\n        code = stock.get(\"代码\", \"\")\n        # 检查代码前缀\n        prefix = code[:3] if len(code) >= 3 else \"\"\n        if prefix in STOCK_CODE_PREFIXES:\n            filtered.append(stock)\n\n    log(f\"筛选后剩余 {len(filtered)} 只股票\")\n    return filtered\n\ndef filter_and_sort(stocks: List[Dict], top_n: int = 50) -> List[Dict]:\n    \"\"\"筛选并排序\"\"\"\n    log(\"正在筛选和排序...\")\n\n    # 先按市场筛选\n    market_filtered = filter_by_market(stocks)\n\n    # 筛选条件\n    filtered = [s for s in market_filtered if s[\"PE\"] > 0 and s[\"PE\"] < 100]\n\n    # 按评分排序\n    sorted_stocks = sorted(filtered, key=lambda x: x[\"评分\"], reverse=True)\n\n    # 返回前N只\n    return sorted_stocks[:top_n]"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":26,"output":452,"cacheRead":63507,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63985,"cost":{"input":0.0000156,"output":0.0009944,"cacheRead":0.0069857700000000005,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007995770000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774487867874}}
