{"type":"message","id":"bc92c93d","parentId":"8bba2100","timestamp":"2026-03-26T02:19:25.422Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要添加获取净利润同比增长率的功能。东方财富通常有财务指标API。让我添加一个函数来获取财务数据。\n\n常见的东方财富财务API：\n- 新浪财经的财务数据接口\n- 东方财富的财务指标接口\n\n我可以尝试使用东方财富的财务数据API。让我添加一个函数来获取净利润同比增长率。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_622e248ac6754a748f160b13","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\stock_analysis.py","oldText":"def safe_float(value, default=0):\n    \"\"\"安全转换浮点数，处理None、\"-\"等无效值\"\"\"\n    if value is None or value == \"\" or value == \"-\":\n        return default\n    try:\n        return float(value)\n    except (ValueError, TypeError):\n        return default","newText":"def safe_float(value, default=0):\n    \"\"\"安全转换浮点数，处理None、\"-\"等无效值\"\"\"\n    if value is None or value == \"\" or value == \"-\":\n        return default\n    try:\n        return float(value)\n    except (ValueError, TypeError):\n        return default\n\ndef get_financial_data(code: str) -> Dict:\n    \"\"\"获取股票财务数据\"\"\"\n    try:\n        # 使用东方财富的财务指标API\n        url = f\"https://push2.eastmoney.com/api/qt/stock/fflow/klt\"\n        params = {\n            \"lmt\": 1,  # 最新一期\n            \"klt\": 1,  # 季报\n            \"secid\": f\"0.{code}\" if code.startswith(\"6\") else f\"1.{code}\",  # 沪市0，深市1\n            \"fields1\": \"f1,f2,f3,f4,f5,f6,f7,f8,f9,f10,f11,f12,f13,f14,f15,f16,f17,f18,f19,f20\",\n            \"ut\": \"bd1d9ddb04089700cf9c27f6f7426281\",\n            \"fltt\": 2\n        }\n        headers = {\n            \"User-Agent\": \"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36\"\n        }\n\n        proxies = {\n            'http': None,\n            'https': None,\n        }\n\n        response = requests.get(url, params=params, headers=headers, timeout=30, proxies=proxies)\n        response.raise_for_status()\n        data = response.json()\n\n       