{"type":"message","id":"88c6e241","parentId":"399e87a3","timestamp":"2026-03-26T03:49:50.430Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_27e1b0fbf3c24cd8876c0270","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    return results\n\ndef filter_by_market(stocks: List[Dict]) -> List[Dict]:\n    \"\"\"根据市场筛选股票\"\"\"\n    log(f\"正在筛选沪市主板和深市主板股票...\")\n    filtered = []\n    for stock in stocks:\n        code = stock.get(\"代码\", \"\")\n        # 检查代码前缀\n        prefix = code[:3] if len(code) >= 3 else \"\"\n        if prefix in STOCK_CODE_PREFIXES:\n            filtered.append(stock)\n\n    log(f\"筛选后剩余 {len(filtered)} 只股票\")\n    return filtered\n\ndef filter_and_sort(stocks: List[Dict], top_n: int = 50) -> List[Dict]:\n    \"\"\"筛选并排序\"\"\"\n    log(\"正在筛选和排序...\")\n\n    # 先按市场筛选\n    market_filtered = filter_by_market(stocks)\n\n    # 筛选条件\n    # 1. PE: 0 < PE < 100\n    # 2. 净利润同比增长率 >= 30%\n    # 3. 营业收入 >= 10亿元\n    filtered = [\n        s for s in market_filtered\n        if s[\"PE\"] > 0\n        and s[\"PE\"] < 100\n        and safe_float(str(s[\"净利润同比增长\"]).rstrip('%')) >= NET_PROFIT_GROWTH_THRESHOLD\n        and safe_float(str(s[\"营业收入\"]).rstrip('亿')) >= REVENUE_THRESHOLD\n    ]\n\n    log(f\"筛选后剩余 {len(filtered)} 只股票（净利润同比增长 >= {NET_PROFIT_GROWTH_THRESHOLD}%，营业收入 >= {REVENUE_THRESHOLD}亿）\")\n\n    # 按评分排序\n    sorted_stocks = sorted(filtered, key=lambda x: x[\"评分\"], reverse=True)\n\n    # 返回前N只\n    return sorted_stocks[:top_n]\n\ndef save_results(stocks: List[Dict], filename: str):\n    \"\"\"保存结果\"\"\"\n    log(f\"正在保存结果到 {filename}...\")\n    with open(filename, \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n        json.dump(stocks, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n    log(f\"结果已保存\")\n\n\n[60 more lines in file. Use offset=350 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774496990425}}
{"type":"message","id":"41012f9e","parentId":"88c6e241","timestamp":"2026-03-26T03:50:12.970Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了，在 filter_and_sort 函数中，它使用 s[\"净利润同比增长\"] 和 s[\"营业收入\"] 来获取这些字段进行筛选。这些字段在 analyze_stocks 函数中已经正确赋值了（营业收入\": f\"{revenue_yuan/10000:.2f}亿\"，净利润同比增长\": f\"{net_profit_growth:.2f}%\"），所以应该是可以工作的。\n\n问题可能是：\n1. 净利润同比增长的值是字符串格式\"xx.xx%\"，需要用 rstrip('%') 去掉%才能转换\n2. 营业收入的值是字符串格式\"xx.xx亿\"，需要用 rstrip('亿') 去掉亿才能转换\n\n让我再测试一次看看能不能正确筛选。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aa72769aa7fc43869f67a850","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\"; python stock_analysis.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":137213,"output":333,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137546,"cost":{"input":0.08232779999999999,"output":0.0007326,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.08306039999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774496990431}}
